<item>
            <title>[HADOOP-10422] Remove redundant logging of RPC retry attempts.</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HADOOP-10422</link>
                <project id="12310240" key="HADOOP">Hadoop Common</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;tt&gt;RetryUtils&lt;/tt&gt; logs each retry attempt at both info level and debug level.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
