                            <comment id="13945870" author="cnauroth" created="Mon, 24 Mar 2014 23:37:27 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I committed this to trunk, branch-2 and branch-2.4.  Nicholas, thank you for the code review.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;blockquote&gt;&lt;p&gt;-1 tests included. The patch doesn&apos;t appear to include any new or modified tests.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This was a change in logging only.  I tested manually by confirming that the redundant log message goes away when running ls, and I also confirmed that it can be turned back on by changing log level to debug.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
